\begin{tabular}{p{2cm} p{14cm}}
ABR & Average Value of Background Region Pixels \\
ANR & Average Value of NearText Region Pixels \\
ATR & Average Value of Text Region  Pixels \\
$ \gamma_{\mathnormal{p}}\mathnormal{(n)}$ & response of a mean filter of pixel $\mathnormal{p}$ with mask size of 2$n$ + 1  $\times$ 2$n$ + 1 \\
$ \rho_\mathnormal{p} $  &  descriptor vector $\{ \gamma_{\mathnormal{p}}(0) , \gamma_{\mathnormal{p}}(1) \dots  \gamma_{\mathnormal{p}}(M)\} $ for a pixel $p$ \\
$ \gamma^{\mathnormal{max}}_{\mathnormal{p}} $& Maximum value of $ \gamma_{\mathnormal{p}}\mathnormal{(n)}$ \\
$ \gamma^{\mathnormal{min}}_{\mathnormal{p}} $& Maximum value of $ \gamma_{\mathnormal{p}}\mathnormal{(n)}$ \\
${\mathnormal{v}}_{\mathnormal{p}} $ &  variation  measured by difference of maximum and minimum values of $\gamma_{\mathnormal{p}}$\\
${\mathnormal{C}}_{\mathnormal{v}}$ & threshold for variation  \\
$ {\mathnormal{R}}_{\mathnormal{\gamma}}$ & strength of the prime element\\
D(u,v) & Normalized distance from centre (x,y) to the point (u,v) \\
$D_o$ & radial center of the band of interest \\
W & width of the band  of interest \\


\end{tabular}
